_sText: Created for this mapping contest: http://www.fpsbanana.com/threads/74207 100% custom brushwork on all the stuff you dont recognize (pagoda, gargoyles) spawn with: T: Deagle & AK CT: Deagle & M4 Snipe areas: 1: pagoda lvl 2 - scout 2: pagoda lvl 3 - AWP Custom Prefabs are available to anybody at request, although I have not added them to the prefab section of the site yet. The Pagoda is 3 levels and highly detailed, and the Gargoyles are moderately detailed, also available as a prefab. Enjoy, and good luck to all contestants!
